    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for a Medium model risk, Medium model influence, Medium decision consequence COU. The single gap — Test conditions achieving level 2 against a required level of 3 — is offset by the multi-laboratory experimental programme (N=11), the favourable UQ campaign results demonstrating robustness across the input parameter space, and the conservative acceptance bounds adopted for normalised error. The overall credibility evidence is sufficient to support regulatory submission.",
